data.description: This one will amaze you! Immaculate water front home located in the desirable Winged Foot subdivision. Convenient location in the heart of daphne close to shopping, dining, easy access to I-10, YMCA, and more. This one owner home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a 2 car garage, and a lovely covered patio with a great view of the community pond. Open concept living space and a split bedroom plan. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances (refrigerator included), loads of cabinets, and a pantry. The primary suite has a view of the pond; the attached bath features a dual sink vanity with granite countertops, soaking tub, separate shower, and a large walk in closet.  Washer and dryer also convey for added convenience! Winged Foot features a neighborhood pool that you will truly enjoy during the summer months!  Pride of ownership is obvious in this home! Schedule a showing before it's too late!  More exterior photos coming soon!
